Class Window

java.lang.Object
  info.gridworld.world.World<Actor>
      info.gridworld.actor.ActorWorld
          Qwerty.Window
Direct Known Subclasses:
PlayerControl, ScrabbleBoard
public class Window
extends ActorWorld

Extends actor world for both PlayerControl and ScrabbleBoard inorder to help set up the GUI involved in both the classes, as the GUI is especially similar. It also contains some generic methods which are used by both PlayerControl and ScrabbleBoard.

Author:
Abhishek, Jeffrey, Aneesh
